MTN Business has added new members to its executive team. Wanda Matandela, the former CEO of Ster-Kinekor, has been appointed as MTN Business Chief Enterprise Business Officer, effective 1 March 2018. Matandela replaces Alpheus Mangale, who served in this role until August 2017. MTN Business has also appointed Christian Wirtz to the position of Executive for Enterprise Solutions and Commercial Management (Group and SA), effective 1 March 2018. Wirtz will manage the overall product portfolio for MTN Business and drive all commercial decisions across all sales segments. “We are very excited to welcome professionals of this calibre to our team,” said Godfrey Motsa, CEO at MTN SA.